{"tid":1648524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔係少咗人！！！","createTime":"2019-10-12T08:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T09:22:00.000Z","uid":72066,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9d1e7dac6f1b3e1783b2409900f769f09b0acfc1","tid":1648524,"uid":72066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"話說之前聽過一個關於亞洲社運抗爭嘅talk，其中一個講者係韓國2016年燭光革命當中「心戰室」嘅領袖。<br />\n<br />\n佢話其實社運參與人數有起有跌係好正常，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係最重要係喺埸運動嘅每個關鍵時刻之前（eg.國會將會通過一啲重要議案），一定要叫到最多嘅人出嚟</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">先可以最有效咁反映民意！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">相信大家都知道嚟緊美國兩個議院都會就《香港人權與民主法案》表決，（喺表決之前我哋一定要再次俾美國睇到我哋嘅決心！！）</span>話俾佢哋知，我哋係未收皮㗎！！唔好俾佢哋覺得香港嘅示威活動已經逐漸減弱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n10月14號，7點遮打，香港人權法造勢大會！！同我逼爆成個中環呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"6d68d13e3393d1ca0de27e216e3fcc8d7a0252dc","tid":1648524,"uid":121589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:59:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7adfe3a8399869417e961b8f949d8a7a62c4493a","tid":1648524,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c33727a88a24db56b5c4d0f0770bf5edad730c7e","tid":1648524,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1a849b907d39253fd8a3dfb49f206d53b7131e5","tid":1648524,"uid":299923,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:00:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e91